    <note>Guo(1) Xun(2) [26461] He was so poor that he could not support his parents. He worked very hard and was not ashamed at wearing poor clothes and eating coarse food and, in the end, was able to obtain an estate (literally land and houses [tiantuo]). His son-in-law, Fan(2) Zuyuan [26462], was also a member of a distinguished lineage. An example of a cycle of mobility. Fan Zuyu, WJ, 38.9b-10a. CBD, 3, 2122-3.</note>
